Tang Na!

225
00:10:47,130 --> 00:10:48,540
After her, after her!

226
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:49,460
Tang Na! Stop running!

227
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,940
Tang Na is over there!

228
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:56,020
All the best, Ding Dong!

229
00:10:56,020 --> 00:10:56,700
All the best!

230
