265
00:12:25,100 --> 00:12:25,890
No, no.

266
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:27,620
We haven't even decided on termination yet.

267
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:28,940
Besides,

268
00:12:28,940 --> 00:12:30,180
